# TC17: LowBatteryDetected3
# Precondition: StandbyMode
# Action: detect battery level below threshold
# Expected: enter LowBatteryMode, motor and cleaner remain stopped
power
expect power on
expect mode StandbyMode
expect motor stopped
expect cleaner off
battery 5
low-battery
expect power on
expect mode LowBatteryMode
expect battery 5
expect motor stopped
expect motorForward false
expect cleaner off
expect cleanerMode off
exit
